{"tid":1727714,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］我地都可以整啲蛇齋餅糭","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:18.000Z","uid":232844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54b54633e095d0613407c50594293cdbeb4131c7","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，其實呢兩三日塞吐露港真係造成幾多不便既。雖然睇得清既自然死都唔會割，但無可否認我地真係會流失一部分淺黃/淺藍既支持，加上啲藍絲同解放軍宜家又走出嚟搬野執野扮好人，變相我地做咗醜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我知會有人話民意冇流失，但就算民意有冇流失，我地都應該要做啲野爭取，就選區議會喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊區議會我地需要大量民意，除咗道歉之外我地都可以做啲野R下啲公公婆婆，尤其係平時<span style=\"color: red;\">攞慣蛇齋餅糭嗰啲</span><br />\n<br />\n拋下磚引下玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">針對吐露港返嗰到工既，可以落街道歉，好似之前機場咁，鞠下躬、派下道歉信/早餐咁。<br />\n<br />\n針對落唔到街/送唔到飯既，可以著黑衫上去探訪、送下米送下水咁。</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論下仲有啲咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcebe385145b6990f23b3aff9e66fdd2c6f3a97c","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37031572c0f5928f806ab11dc5ad498e8c13abc","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb3a79d73af8f9e9723a92b69f9fcfdba28183f","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"8b81309ab593fad956e4c09eb5d4d0d8161b5a2a","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f73352d804bbfbba5d08b19c4bc0a8b8377e4b","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"40f69bf4ca1cbc2f25bf05140f5471f50ec68840","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfefa2a1329e6b2246c8e8de2162cd7dc5d34ec","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"仲有八日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0a8b377c21360d26a4869c01429a7dfaa04b1a","tid":1727714,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"道乜春歉<br />\n又要下跪俾人打？未試過？"},{"pid":"2e0c88493a41f5ac700423805233c211128c5c23","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"我知道五個月以嚟啲人都埋哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃既黃藍既藍"},{"pid":"2d820355a11dbb8a6b7ed8a489f3c97129d785db","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"中立撚同港豬係好可惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢地都有得投票係事實"},{"pid":"c6e26e0c72a49a9702482f7bc90844592728c19f","tid":1727714,"uid":232844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0a8b377c21360d26a4869c01429a7dfaa04b1a","tid":1727714,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"道乜春歉<br />\n又要下跪俾人打？未試過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔一定要道歉 但點都要做啲野去爭民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}